											<%= image_tag 'maintenance-innerpage-icon-big.png', :class => 'img-responsive', :alt => 'Services Image' %>
										</div>
										<div class="web-content-para">
											<p>Your website is the mirror of your businesses and like any mirror can develop cracks, so can your business. WebEnrich believes that bad codes and faulty website design can damage your online presence.</p>
											<p>WebEnrich's website maintenance and support services cater to diverse range of problems that your business could face. Our professionals are always prepared to solve any crack that your business may develop, before it actually does.</p>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
