			<div class="container">
				<div class="col-md-12">
					<div class="row">
						<div class="col-md-12 mobile-content">
							<h2>Our Services</h2>
							<ul class="mobile-services">
								<li>Elimination of irrelevant and extra codes</li>
								<li>Updating the content on your website from time to time</li>
								<li>Changing the graphics to match the revised text</li>
								<li>Solving any urgent technical issues your website may face instantly.</li>
							</ul>
							<p>We also provide you with a comprehensive report of all that we've done. This makes our business solutions sophisticated, cost effective and very much in demand!</p>
